# =============================================================================
# CSP policy value — per-environment. Author: meesell-infra-builder (SP07 / D42).
#
# OWNERSHIP: the ALLOWLIST CONTENT below is FRONTEND-OWNED (spec_sp07_infra.md §1.1,
# the Native-Federation + es-module-shims + Angular + PrimeNG/Tailwind requirement).
# Infra owns only the MECHANISM that emits it (nginx add_header / Traefik Middleware)
# and the per-env templating. If the frontend lead revises the allowlist after the
# dev smoke (spec §2(A) iterate-on-dev), update the values here in lockstep — do NOT
# invent infra-side tokens.
#
# This file is SOURCED by docker-entrypoint.sh, which selects the right CSP_POLICY
# for $APP_ENV and runs `envsubst` over nginx.conf.template.
#
# THREE ENVIRONMENTS:
#   dev      — shell + 6 remotes served from LOCALHOST (ng serve ports 4201-4206)
#              during the dev CSP smoke (spec §2). 'self' covers the shell origin;
#              the localhost remote origins are explicitly allowlisted so the smoke
#              proves the mechanism end-to-end before any hosted surface exists.
#   staging  — remotes-staging.mesell.xyz + the staging API host.
#   prod     — remotes.mesell.xyz + api.mesell.xyz (V1.5; prod namespace deferred).
#
# Per spec §1.1: 'wasm-unsafe-eval' for script-src and 'unsafe-inline' for style-src
# are the pragmatic V1 choices (es-module-shims / Angular runtime + Tailwind/PrimeNG
# runtime <style> injection). CONFIRM each token EMPIRICALLY on dev (spec §2(A)).
# Prefer a per-response nonce over 'unsafe-inline' for SCRIPTS if the dev smoke shows
# it is feasible; styles stay 'unsafe-inline' (style nonces are impractical with
# Angular component styles).
# =============================================================================

# --- DEV (localhost-served remotes; the smoke surface) ----------------------
# Remotes served by `ng serve` on 4201-4206 → http://localhost:<port>. The shell
# origin during the smoke is http://localhost:4200 (or the dev shell host). We
# allowlist the localhost remote origins + the dev API.
CSP_POLICY_dev="default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' http://localhost:4201 http://localhost:4202 http://localhost:4203 http://localhost:4204 http://localhost:4205 http://localhost:4206; connect-src 'self' https://api.mesell.xyz http://localhost:4201 http://localhost:4202 http://localhost:4203 http://localhost:4204 http://localhost:4205 http://localhost:4206; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' http://localhost:4201 http://localhost:4202 http://localhost:4203 http://localhost:4204 http://localhost:4205 http://localhost:4206; font-src 'self' data: http://localhost:4201 http://localhost:4202 http://localhost:4203 http://localhost:4204 http://localhost:4205 http://localhost:4206; img-src 'self' data: http://localhost:4201 http://localhost:4202 http://localhost:4203 http://localhost:4204 http://localhost:4205 http://localhost:4206; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'"

# --- STAGING (remotes-staging.mesell.xyz off-cluster CDN) --------------------
CSP_POLICY_staging="default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' https://remotes-staging.mesell.xyz; connect-src 'self' https://staging-api.mesell.xyz https://remotes-staging.mesell.xyz; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://remotes-staging.mesell.xyz; font-src 'self' data: https://remotes-staging.mesell.xyz; img-src 'self' data: https://remotes-staging.mesell.xyz; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'"

# --- PROD (remotes.mesell.xyz off-cluster CDN; V1.5) ------------------------
CSP_POLICY_prod="default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' https://remotes.mesell.xyz; connect-src 'self' https://api.mesell.xyz https://remotes.mesell.xyz; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://remotes.mesell.xyz; font-src 'self' data: https://remotes.mesell.xyz; img-src 'self' data: https://remotes.mesell.xyz; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'"
